{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/give-a-background-color-to-a-div-element","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-css","demoType":null,"title":"Dodeli Pozadinsku Boju div Elementu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Mozete postaviti boju pozadine elementa pomocu svojstva <code>background-color</code>.</p>\n<p>Na primer, ako zelite da boja pozadine elementa bude <code>green</code>, ovo biste napisali u <code>style</code> elementu:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">.green-background {\n  background-color: green;\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"bad87fed1348bd9aede07836","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napravite klasu <code>silver-background</code> sa <code>background-color</code> vrednoscu <code>silver</code>. Dodelite tu klasu svom <code>div</code> elementu.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cdRKMCk","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18190,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/give-a-background-color-to-a-div-element"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n<style>\n  .red-text {\n    color: red;\n  }\n\n  h2 {\n    font-family: Lobster, monospace;\n  }\n\n  p {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-family: monospace;\n  }\n\n  .thick-green-border {\n    border-color: green;\n    border-width: 10px;\n    border-style: solid;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n  }\n\n  .smaller-image {\n    width: 100px;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<h2 class=\"red-text\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\n<main>\n  <p class=\"red-text\">Click here to view more <a href=\"#\">cat photos</a>.</p>\n\n  <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"smaller-image thick-green-border\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n\n  <div>\n    <p>Things cats love:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>catnip</li>\n      <li>laser pointers</li>\n      <li>lasagna</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\n    <ol>\n      <li>flea treatment</li>\n      <li>thunder</li>\n      <li>other cats</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label><br>\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" checked> Loving</label>\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Energetic</label><br>\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n  </form>\n</main>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vas <code>div</code> element treba da ima klasu <code>silver-background</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('div').classList.contains('silver-background'));"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>div</code> element treba da ima srebrnu boju pozadine.</p>","testString":"const div = document.querySelector('div');\nconst backgroundColor = window.getComputedStyle(div)['background-color']; \nassert.strictEqual(backgroundColor, 'rgb(192, 192, 192)');"},{"text":"<p>Klasa <code>silver-background</code> treba da bude definisana u <code>style</code> elementu, a <code>background-color</code> treba da ima vrednost <code>silver</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(__helpers.removeHtmlComments(code), /\\.silver-background\\s*{\\s*background-color\\s*:\\s*silver\\s*;?\\s*}/);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"